  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2563800/extras/d148188778aea2fc06bb7cc8c63c58dc.avif?t=1761602811\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2563800/extras_big/d148188778aea2fc06bb7cc8c63c58dc.avif?t=1761602811 width=800 height=234 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Balance risk and reward as your make your choices! Push your luck to grow your build, but don't overestimate your abilities, or your run could end on the spot. Navigate the dungeon wisely and reap the rewards to optimize your build to crush the dungeon with 13 unique characters!​</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2563800/extras/1972c5ba305a6ea7369408977ae95fb4.avif?t=1761602811\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2563800/extras_big/1972c5ba305a6ea7369408977ae95fb4.avif?t=1761602811 width=800 height=234 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 130 unique items can be mixed and matched to create a devastating build, laying waste to every enemy in sight! Be careful not to hurt yourself with an item that doesn't fit, and experiment with synergies to become an overpowered behemoth!​</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2563800/extras/d6431b8d8db630a3fd9caa43869b4e48.avif?t=1761602811\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2563800/extras_big/d6431b8d8db630a3fd9caa43869b4e48.avif?t=1761602811 width=800 height=234 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover the secrets of the dungeon on your quest to slay the Villain to unlock hidden paths, uncover new items, and grow your band of adventurers! And for those who crave a challenge, the greatest rewards are locked behind the greatest trials!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2563800/extras/b002910782e2427384bc336001d3ec65.avif?t=1761602811\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2563800/extras_big/b002910782e2427384bc336001d3ec65.avif?t=1761602811 width=800 height=234 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play solo or with friends in local co-op, with up to 4 people! Combine character abilities to improve your odds, or do a mild amount of trolling, the choice is yours!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please note that extra controllers are required to play with others.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2563800/extras/d148188778aea2fc06bb7cc8c63c58dc.avif?t=1761602811\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2563800/extras_big/d148188778aea2fc06bb7cc8c63c58dc.avif?t=1761602811 width=800 height=234 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Balance risk and reward as your make your choices! Push your luck to grow your build, but don't overestimate your abilities, or your run could end on the spot. Navigate the dungeon wisely and reap the rewards to optimize your build to crush the dungeon with 13 unique characters!​</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2563800/extras/1972c5ba305a6ea7369408977ae95fb4.avif?t=1761602811\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2563800/extras_big/1972c5ba305a6ea7369408977ae95fb4.avif?t=1761602811 width=800 height=234 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 130 unique items can be mixed and matched to create a devastating build, laying waste to every enemy in sight! Be careful not to hurt yourself with an item that doesn't fit, and experiment with synergies to become an overpowered behemoth!​</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2563800/extras/d6431b8d8db630a3fd9caa43869b4e48.avif?t=1761602811\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2563800/extras_big/d6431b8d8db630a3fd9caa43869b4e48.avif?t=1761602811 width=800 height=234 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover the secrets of the dungeon on your quest to slay the Villain to unlock hidden paths, uncover new items, and grow your band of adventurers! And for those who crave a challenge, the greatest rewards are locked behind the greatest trials!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2563800/extras/b002910782e2427384bc336001d3ec65.avif?t=1761602811\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2563800/extras_big/b002910782e2427384bc336001d3ec65.avif?t=1761602811 width=800 height=234 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play solo or with friends in local co-op, with up to 4 people! Combine character abilities to improve your odds, or do a mild amount of trolling, the choice is yours!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please note that extra controllers are required to play with others.</p>",
